values: Hey..I'm changing my journal name to indierock07, and it's still at livejournal. So, if you would add me to your friends list on that name instead, that would be great!

So..I just got back from driving a little while ago. I need some more practice though.. I went over the curb a few times while trying to make right turns..but thats fine I guess..need more practice. It's pretty fun to drive. I want my license right now! ..

I hope the sun comes out soon! It's been rainy out for a few days now..blah.

So..some of my friends left for D.C. yesterday. I kinda wish I could of went..oh well. 

Yeah...this is a small update..but I have a frozen pizza in the oven and it's ready. I've gotta go take it out!! Adios amigos! :)

Well I'm new to livejournal, because I had a greatestjournal before. Someone told me that the people are really cool at livejournal, so I'm gonna try this journal. 

If you want to add me as a friend, comment and I will add you back! 

Bye for now! :)
